org.digijava.kernel.ampapi.endpoints.common

Class JsonApiResponse<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.kernel.ampapi.endpoints.errors.ApiErrorResponse
      • org.digijava.kernel.ampapi.endpoints.common.JsonApiResponse<T>

  • public class JsonApiResponse<T>
extends ApiErrorResponse
    A generic EP Response that can be used to store commonly reported errors and warnings in the same format by all AMP EPs, as well as any additional generic details or concrete class with response content.

    Note that details/content will be reported unwrapped for convenience.
